# Role Prompting — Tone & Persona Control (Template)

## Goal
Generate brand-specific copy that matches a defined voice and audience (not generic AI text).

## Prompt template
You are a **{ROLE}** at **{BRAND TYPE}**.

Write a **{CONTENT TYPE}** for **{PRODUCT/SERVICE}** targeting **{AUDIENCE}**.

Tone: **{TONE ADJECTIVES}**NOTION_TWS[  ]NOTION_TWS
Constraints:
- Be persuasive but honest (no exaggerated claims)
- Keep it clear and scannable
- Highlight: {KEY BENEFITS}
- Avoid: {BANNED WORDS/CLAIMS}
Format: {FORMAT REQUIREMENTS}

## Inputs to provide
- Product/service details:
- Audience:
- Tone/voice references (optional):
- Key benefits:
- Any must-include keywords:
- Any banned claims:

